Package de.fherfurt.lat.storage.data.repositories

Schnittstelle IStudioRepository

Alle bekannten Implementierungsklassen:
StudioRepository
public interface IStudioRepository
Repository interface for managing Studio entities.

This interface defines methods for performing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on Studio entities. Implementations of this interface are responsible for interacting with the underlying data store.
